<subSubSection id="C78C36BA52B346FADD20EE45CE85BD7B" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="614042731AD80E551CE72CF9E30263BE" pageNumber="496">Etymology L rectitrudis, erect pike or pointed pole, alluding to propodeal spines.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D5276907134AE9A15D595128985A7C19" type="diagnosis">
